criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients, male or female, 18 years or older;

          -  Patients with de-novo coronary lesions and slated to receive a Promus Element stent;

          -  Patients who are slated to undergo IVUS after stent deployment during implantation
             procedure

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients receiving more than one drug-eluting stent within the same lesion during
             implantation procedure;

          -  Patients with in-stent restenosis;

          -  Patients who had IVUS imaging attained with manual pullback.
